"url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK"}],"roleHeading":"Class","externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","symbolKind":"class","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"well as in energy saving mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"video frames per second."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:"}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/detectionRate","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/energySaveDetectionRate","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/inactivityTimeout","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/isEnergySavingEnabled","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/keepScreenOn","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/motionSensitivity"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/notifyPropertiesChange()"],"anchor":"Instance-Methods","title":"Instance Methods"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/defaultConfiguration"],"anchor":"Type-Properties","title":"Type Properties"}],"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/init":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/docume